data.description: *Interest rate buydown assistance available?* Come tour this inviting, freshly painted 3-bedroom home with 2.5 bathrooms and a bonus Finished Room Over Garage (FROG) on a spacious 3-acre lot. The first-floor primary bedroom features a stunning ensuite bathroom with garden tub, while the open concept living area boasts a cozy fireplace. A detached garage with electrical hookup and side concrete pad give you additional space for your recreational vehicles. Enjoy the sunrises and sunsets on your wrap around porch and back deck.
